Class UploadProgress

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.punchthrough.bean.sdk.message.UploadProgress

  • public abstract class UploadProgress
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the upload progress of a Bean's upload in progress. Returned in the onUpdate Callback passed into Bean.programWithSketch(com.punchthrough.bean.sdk.upload.SketchHex, Callback, Runnable).
